Public NotInheritable Class PowerShellChannelWriter Inherits BaseChannelWriter

Docs.summary: ChannelWrite is the concrete implementation of IChannelWrite. It writes all the traces to the specified traceChannel. TraceChannel is specified in the constructor. It always uses PowerShell event provider Id.
